  "description": "This individual is a middle-aged human of bronze skin, marked by a long, healed cleft along the left brow that draws the face into a permanent asymmetry. Gray eyes sit deep under heavy orbital ridges, while brown hair is kept in a shortknot that emphasizes a thick neck and broad, ship-hardened shoulders. The nose shows an old break set slightly off-center, and the jawline carries the blunt squareness typical of lifelong exposure to hard labor and close-quarters violence. Overall proportions are compact and powerful, built for command at sea rather than ornament.",
